Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你拿到多少壓歲錢了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島應該有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿穀你拿到多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十歲以上的人收聖誕禮物和壓歲錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法律是不允許的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.68,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz285.015\pos(211,296)\c&H172E20&}媽媽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊 那怎麼可…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十歲以後就不能拿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 真島拿了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一萬五千日元吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違法!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:52.47,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\pos(765,197)\frz260.045}怎麼可能有拿那麼多的\N孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:52.47,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\frz278.939\pos(406,72)}那是他爸爸的\N年終獎數額啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:52.47,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\pos(215,145)\frz290.84}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.47,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(856,578)}壓歲錢 完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能拿到那麼多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他爸爸的年終獎數額吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:57.51,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(864,897)\pos(490,281)}紅葉漫小倉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊 這不就是百人一首嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學你會這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說會不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校每年都會舉辦歌留多大會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來比吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是沒有人來讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有磁帶啊 磁帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…怎麼弄來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把25張牌分成三段排好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到上句讀出來 就要拿掉下句對應的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只是個歌留多比賽而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種眼神…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋來紅葉散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.52,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あらしふく…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多…以前是這樣玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要搶到一張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張牌的上句我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「激流戲淺水 岩前兩紛飛」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.33,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}せをはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要搶到那一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.05,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「激…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以代替綿谷同學比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正千早絕對更弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替綿谷同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:52.04,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}しろきをみれば　よぞふけにける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:52.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「更深烏啼晚 繁霜滿清霄」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「代替」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是「我」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己要贏太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和太一的比賽 我覺得非常有意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多太好玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和綿谷同學比賽的時候就不是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是要成為名人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 綾瀨同學就是女王咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女性之中 最強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王…
