Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天衣無縫」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}天衣無縫（日語）：不做作，非常天真自然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 甚麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那肉包小子就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「烤肉套餐（大份）」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼駒野說白了就是…
