Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.89,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H606367&\frz260.538\pos(248,433)}甚麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.89,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H606367&\frz342.99\pos(244,498)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 用那麼美的詞語形容我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要形容部長嗎? 嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「器…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「器用貧乏」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}器用貧乏（日語）：甚麼事都能做點，但不成大器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想逗逗大家笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H523D51&\an7\pos(794,77)\frz257.218}挺不錯的啊 太一 \N說得很對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\frz277.512\pos(241,58)\c&H3E3543&}這不是在傷口上撒鹽嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\c&H3E3543&\pos(35,110)\frz281.886}你還真是「天衣無縫」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\c&H3E3543&\pos(59,290)\frz8.553}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺不錯的啊太一 說得很對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器用貧乏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的活動室就是這裏啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我再三懇求女帝才拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雜物室嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到處都是塵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼多意見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老師說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果達到五個部員 就正式承認你們這個部」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「也給你們配指導老師」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的三個人 找不找得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對能找到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.90,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むらさめの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「驟雨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是歌留多?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多這東西…我怎麼可能玩得來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒那種天賦!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不一樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會學習…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有書桌這一片天地啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選同伴的話 比起歌留多的天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更願意選在榻榻米上 不斷努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有經驗的人就給我加入歌留多部啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有經驗的人就給我加入歌留多部吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「因為湊齊了5個成員 所以請求正式成立歌留多部」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長要換成綾瀨同學以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顧問暫時就由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.65,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,おとにきく…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「高師濱雖名…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.49,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆふされば…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「暮色沉田野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早…這樣果然還是不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實力相距太懸殊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛開始玩歌留多的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手也是個特別強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他當時手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不可能變得這麼喜歡歌留多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我也不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想讓大家變強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候我們五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去參加團體戰的全國大會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.40,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤①
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.65,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤②
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.91,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤③
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:23.54,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,100)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤④
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子他…在哪兒買的T恤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐喜歡絲網印刷 甚麼圖案都能做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}即在絲網上覆蓋鏤空的圖案，然後用可以\N滲透過網格的顏料把圖案印上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也讓她幫你們倆做T恤吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.92,subtitle_16,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2C2F42&\fs50\pos(303,437)}超大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用麻煩了 好意心領了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}肉包小子真的不用啦 我們穿得普普通通就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我才不喜歡做這種衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人苦苦央求我才做的啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 想做隊服的話就告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傲嬌?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批…批薩包子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}包子裏面放類似批薩的餡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz266.622\pos(1084,126)}需要隊服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz347.445\pos(1088,225)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz283.57\pos(901,363)}我給你們做好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz284.319\pos(877,405)}要好好利用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz343.871\pos(907,487)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz258.769\pos(272,247)}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz339.917\pos(265,322)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\shad0\3c&H65618A&\c&H726FD4&\fad(300,0)}瑞 澤 高 中 GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 西田!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有好好給你姐說明團體戰的規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.54,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（從左到右）男生S碼 女生L碼 男生L碼 男生M碼 女生S碼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼設計的話 出場順序豈不是只能有這一種了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外想問一下為甚麼選這順序了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是按姐姐對樣貌的喜歡順序排的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後一名?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒數第二?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器用貧乏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 第一名!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HD2CEC9&\pos(1216,101)\frz265.173}是為甚麼呢\N 感覺有人看著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H422878&\pos(920,209)\frz278.328}心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz277.885\pos(205,479)}鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(217,529)}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為甚麼呢…感覺有人看著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖•定•♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:37.36,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}男生間的悄悄話①
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨和小奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做女朋友的話 哪個好?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選小奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島你太狡猾了! 快說啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用顧忌啦 你絕對也是選小奏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨那種根本是不可能的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\t(0,200,\fs30)\c&H4231C2&\3c&H353749&\shad0\a6}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.38,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H28231D&\pos(207,90)}做女朋友的話選誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.38,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H123332&\pos(618,495)}不可能 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:59.34,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}男生間的悄悄話② — 太一反擊篇 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胸部吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是看上了大江同學的巨乳吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話我們可沒說過啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳…乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝言差矣!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏長得可愛 性格也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她去約會的情景是可以想像的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟綾瀨的約會根本沒法想像!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會變成去練習歌留多的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就是就是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}說到底巨乳就是正義啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 綾瀨絕對沒門!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:24.66,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H28231D&\pos(207,90)}做女朋友的話選誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:24.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H123332&\pos(622,469)}歌留多癡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是瑞澤高中的順序表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛小子 睫毛小子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說啦 你們打入決賽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千早也在最佳狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來都不知道 千早也會感到有壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 千早也會?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為千早總是很強勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我選擇了錯誤的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓她變得那麼脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我居然連千早都不瞭解」…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得接受這個事實對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我 是部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣 所以我才一直注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就算賭上全部青春 也不可能變得比新更強」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}回想起你們習慣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在這裏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒問題 絕對能行的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是另外一個你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かぜをいたみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「萬浪奔卷去…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまはただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「苦戀不得允…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.40,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つくばねの…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「築波男女川…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你不說「對不起」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搶到一張了! 太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨 連我都能搶到敵陣的牌了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎麼能在進攻上輸給別人!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊守住了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下一張一定要搶到!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張牌就只是一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:17.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}こひぞつもりて　ふちとなりぬる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:17.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「情愫亦細始 歷久成浩淵」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為隊伍搶下一張!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.52,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わすらるる…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「海約已相違…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色潤原野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あはぢしま…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鴴棲淡路島…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.90,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みよしのの…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋風肅吉野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮 西田!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有決定字的變化我絕對不會弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為大家的支柱!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:47.18,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いかにひさしき　ものとかはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:47.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「宵苦夜難盡 此艱君怎知」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯錯這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張也不允許!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.93,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よもすがら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「意迷芳心亂…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤一勝!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤兩勝!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬萊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張一張地搶到手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣結束的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你得躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽已經棄權了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄權…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 都說不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老實呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也沒用 你已經回不去比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明努力過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家約好了…要贏下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這是做甚麼呢 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼好道歉的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨 我今天第一次獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 而且還是二連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在複賽的淘汰賽中輸給了富士崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好想再賽幾場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體狀態不能馬上恢復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭明早第一班新幹線回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還按捺不住興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以完美的身體狀態迎戰明天的個人賽!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮詩暢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是史上最年輕的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.94,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はなさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山風…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.07,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…そふ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…邀櫻散」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這戰況 又來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經差了十張了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮詩暢 果然等級不同啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生也快喪失鬥志了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也不弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該能以不遜于女王的速度 搶下她盯上的牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是場上的牌有幾十張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法把全場的都盯住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…難道說女王能做到嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想像自己獲勝的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事還是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能在拼勁上 輸給12歲時候的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.71,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにはえの…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「羈旅與君會…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說不相上下嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.02,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふくからに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枯風遠山至…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.11,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「神代有蓬萊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20號搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直僵硬的身體 活動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得更自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這競技線當中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使面對強大得讓身體都僵硬的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能自如地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難以表達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所謂「強大」就是這個意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只搶到了五張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和女王的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二十張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗記必須更完美 不然使不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆直 迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細地聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加 更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣做才能贏她…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於在此刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作了真正的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:56.50,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}女生間的悄悄話①
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.50,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(685,109,681,109,0,480)\frz283.098\fad(400,0)}同班同學 \N小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小千和小奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要和歌留多部的其中一個人交往 你們會選誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我想也用不著問啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 恭喜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.89,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs25\bord0\c&H322D28&\pos(461,52)}恭喜•獨佔鰲頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.64,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}女生間的悄悄話②
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.64,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(675,50,672,50,0,280)\frz283.098\fad(400,0)}想聊戀愛\N話題的小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦! 我問的是男生!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問要和男生交往的話會選誰!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不限於歌留多部也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真回答沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊! 慢著!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對正片造成影響的 你還是別說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.95,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H465052&\move(519,360,531,302)\frz262.448}後面還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.95,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.669\pos(178,429)}原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:44.49,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)}我就算沒在這個環節出場 也不會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再用四字熟語描述一下對朋友的印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.49,subtitle_16,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H343434&\fs40\bord0\pos(740,418)\frz276.671}心無旁騖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可別再說甚麼「烤肉套餐」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}（感覺還是這個文言中\N表肯定的詞最貼切…）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒野啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「頭腦明晰」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}頭腦明晰（日語）：頭腦靈活，才智出眾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏則是「才色兼備」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}才色兼備（日語）：有才華，\N有美貌，即才貌雙全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒野同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「眉目秀麗」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}眉目秀麗（日語）：即眉清目秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「豬突猛進」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}豬突猛進（日語）：指不考慮周圍的人和情況，\N一味像豬一樣以迅猛的勢頭前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這詞足以概括千早了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子是…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「養豚狗肉」?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話應該是「羊頭狗肉」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}羊頭狗肉（日語）：實質和外表不一致，\N即掛羊頭賣狗肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為甚麼是這個熟語?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}「養豚」和「羊頭」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為想不到其他的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說綾瀨你居然若無其事地說我是豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}日語中「豚」即指豬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以上這些 今年也請多多指教咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(787,146)}我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(775,278)}無法記住全部百人一首的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(732,241)}是蟲豸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz8.838\pos(831,463)\c&HE1CDFE&}須
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE7E4E6&\frz260.236\move(317,432,337,342,0,120)\fad(100,0)}下周再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.99,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H535360&\frz349.184\pos(216,349)}浩
